('Look at this sentence: "The cat runs fast." Which word tells us HOW the cat runs?', 'multiple_choice', 'reading', 'Grade 1', 'us', '["cat", "runs", "fast", "the"]', 'fast', 'The word "fast" describes how the cat runs. It is an adverb.', 2, 1),
