('Read this passage: "Birds build nests in many different ways. Some birds use twigs and leaves. Other birds use mud and grass. Each type of bird has its own special way of making a home." What is the main idea?', 'multiple_choice', 'reading', 'Grade 2', 'us', '["Birds eat different foods", "Birds build nests in different ways", "Birds live in trees", "Birds can fly"]', 'Birds build nests in different ways', 'The passage is about how different birds build their nests differently.', 2, 2),
('After reading the bird passage, write a paragraph explaining two different ways birds build nests. Use details from the passage.', 'essay', 'reading', 'Grade 2', 'us', '[]', '', 'Student should mention twigs/leaves and mud/grass, showing comprehension of passage details.', 3, 3),
('If you have 15 stickers and give away 8 stickers to friends, how many stickers do you have left?', 'short_answer', 'math', 'Grade 2', 'us', '[]', '7', 'Subtraction: 15 - 8 = 7 stickers remaining.', 2, 2),

