('Read this paragraph: "Maria loves to read mystery books. She enjoys trying to solve the puzzle before the main character does. Last week, she read three mystery books and solved two of the mysteries correctly." Based on this passage, what can you infer about Maria?', 'multiple_choice', 'reading', 'Grade 3', 'us', '["She dislikes reading", "She is good at solving puzzles", "She only reads one book per week", "She never solves mysteries"]', 'She is good at solving puzzles', 'The passage shows Maria enjoys mystery puzzles and successfully solved 2 out of 3, indicating skill.', 3, 2),
